title: Arbor Skateboards :: Tyler Howell
description:
Arbor Skateboards is proud to announce our newest team rider – Tyler Howell!
A Santa Barbara local, Tyler Howell takes a naturally fluid California style of downhill skating and matches it with his powerful and technical determination. His approach is unique and gives a new look for skaters to aspire to.
In his first video with Arbor (film/edit Jack Boston), Tyler demonstrates what it means to skate hard and fast on the Santa Barbara Mountains. He is riding the 2013 Vugenhausen as his preferred board for these mountain roads.
Now enjoy as you see the chill vibes of Santa Barabara get paired with Johnny Cash and some downhill skateboarding.
To see more of Arbor Skateboards visit: 
arborcollective.com/skateboards
